  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective is to evaluate the efficacy of a web-trained workforce of Hispanic and African
      American diabetes peer mentors delivering Diabetes Self-Management Support (DSMS) to patients
      with poorly-controlled diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
